title: Club not showing
body: I have only just recently realised that the club that I created (R3ND) is not showing up in my league client. I confirmed with my clan that only 1 member is seeing the clan in the client.

replies.body:
Submit a ticket to player support: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new

They should be able to help you further.
